<div class="footer-wikiwalk-nav">
<p style="text-align: center;">&#171; <a href="/2014-survey-results">2014</a> | <a href="/2015-survey-results">2015</a> | <span style="color: blue">2016</span> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/2017-survey-results">2017</a> | <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/2018-survey-results">2018</a> &#187;</p>
